videos.description: Nneka Ogwumike says the Sparks won the WNBA championship for Candace Parker, who has had an emotional season.

tracking.trackingName: COM_WNBA Interview (Ogwumike dedicates WNBA title to Parker) 2016/10/20 espnW

videos.headline: Ogwumike dedicates WNBA title to Parker

videos.description: After a Game 4 loss to the Lynx, Magic Johnson told the Sparks the series wasn't over and they just had to believe. Johnson praises Minnesota and breaks down Los Angeles' WNBA title season.

tracking.trackingName: COM_WNBA Interview (Magic had words of wisdom for Sparks before Game 5) 2016/10/20 espnW

videos.headline: Magic had words of wisdom for Sparks before Game 5

videos.description: Lynx coach Cheryl Reeve is livid about the officiating after Game 5 of the WNBA Finals, where she believes Nneka Ogwumike's shot came after the clock expired and should have been reviewed.

tracking.trackingName: COM_WNBA Interview (Lynx coach fired up with officiating) 2016/10/20 ESHEET

videos.headline: Lynx coach fired up with officiating
